		<p>
		  In order to be able to use session variables, we need to tell PHP that we want to use sessions on this page.  To do this, we call the <a href="http://us2.php.net/function.session-start">session_start()</a> built-in function at the top of the script.
		  The following is the code that we used on this page to create the variable:		  
		</p>
		
		<pre style="background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 10px; padding:10px;">		
